               <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX> The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DSM</ENAMEX> changes its mind about what
it's going to call mental <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">disorders</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">every few years</TIMEX>, so obviously we can't
