"<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Antisocial Personality Disorder</ENAMEX>" is not really what the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DSM</ENAMEX> says it is,
is like arguing that <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Madame Bovary</ENAMEX> didn't really do all those things Flaubert
said she did. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Antisocial Personality Disorder</ENAMEX> is its <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DSM</ENAMEX>
